Package waz.contract.factory

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ContractSubscriber
    The Contract Subscriber is the observer used to broadcast event made by subscribers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContractAggregator  
    ContractFactory
    The factory is a contract used to create transaction using the pattern Dao.
    ContractPublisher
    As subject, the Contract Publisher is used to perform operation made or demand by users to execute many types of unit transactions.
    Subscriber
    Concrete Observer who observes the subject and perform operation bound to the subject specification.
    TopicSubject
    This class defines the real subject observed by subscribers to perform operation and notify this subscriber.
